        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "後半戦、エースの投入によって一気に点差を稼ぐ戦略が功を奏した。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "彼は地道なロビー活動によって、法案成立に必要な賛成票を稼いだ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "試験の配点が高い後半の記述問題で、確実に得点を稼いでおきたい。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「へへっ、このトリックなら審査員のポイントをかなり稼げるはずだぜ」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 3,
        "gloss": "to work hard (at one's job)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "「おっ、今日も朝から精が出るね！しっかり稼いで家族を喜ばせてやりなよ」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "彼は将来の独立という目標のために、今は脇目も振らずに現場で稼いでいる。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "かつての炭鉱町では、多くの男たちが一攫千金を夢見て必死に稼いでいた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      }
